subSubSection.paragraph:
Four subspecies have been recognized in 

O. aterrimus

: 

O. a. aterrimus

from China and Vietnam; 

O. a. erythropus

(Bingham, 1897) from India, Myanmar, Laos, and Thailand; 

O. a. khasianus

(Cameron, 1900) from India; and 

O. a. nigriceps

van der Vecht, 1963 from China and Vietnam (
van der Vecht 1963
; 
Kumar and Sharma 2012
; 
Selis 2018
; 
Truong et al. 2019
).

